high_descs: Turn around and walk along the left side of the table, then turn right and face the table.
Pick up the glass on the table.
Turn left and walk ahead, veering right to the sink.
Wash the glass in the sink.
Turn left and walk to the counter, then turn left and walk all the way to the shelves on the other side of the room.
Place the glass on the shelf next to the dirty plate.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed glass on a shelf.

high_descs: Turn around right and head towards the table on your right.
Pick up the glass cup from the edge of the table.
Turn left across the the room then face the sink .
Put the glass cup in sink, open the tap of water and rinse the glass cup.
Pick up the glass cup and turn left and head towards dish rack.
Put the glass cup in the dish rack.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean glass cup in the dish rack.

high_descs: Turn right, hang a right at the wall and walk to the silver counter on the right.
Pick up the dirty glass from the right corner of the counter.
Turn left, hang a right around the counter and walk to the sink to the left.
Put the dirty glass inside the sink, rinse it for a few seconds, and pick it back up.
Turn left, hang a left at the counter and walk to the rack of wooden shelves against the wall.
Put the clean glass on the middle shelf on the right side on the rack.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean glass on a shelf.
